            "longitude": -50.000002
          }
        }
      },
      "source": "synthetic",
      "_note": "In-bounds synthetic: lon=-50.0 IEEE-754 LE (bytes 0,0,72,194) at offsets 8-11, lat=-40.0 IEEE-754 LE (bytes 0,0,32,194) at offsets 12-15; alarmLevel via byte[19]>>4, alarmBattery via byte[20]&0x0f. Expected lat/lon (-40.000001 / -50.000002) are the values produced by running reference/upstream-codec.js (its hex2float is an approximation), then normalized to the vocabulary."
